snippet.title: Become an Aethermancer - Adventurer Trailer
snippet.description:
"Well, hello there! Are you also here to save the world from the Void?"

Become an Aethermancer, guide a team of monsters beyond death and fight your way through the Void! Aethermancer is a monster taming roguelite RPG with turnbased 3v3 battles.

Wishlist Aethermancer on Steam to be notified once the demo releases:
https://s.team/a/2288470/
